<p>However, it’s crucial to remember that respectful flirtation is key.  This means keeping the messages tasteful and appropriate, avoiding anything that could make your husband uncomfortable or feel pressured.  The goal is to create a feeling of playful anticipation and shared intimacy, not to cause anxiety or embarrassment. Charming interest is expressed through playful language, suggestive innuendo (but not outright suggestive), and a genuine tone of affection.  These messages can be incredibly effective in building connection, reminding your husband of your affection, and strengthening your bond.</p>
    

